## Identifikation der Top-Terms für jedes Thema

#### 📋 Exercise 1.2: Visualisierung der Themenprävalenz



::: {.cell output-location='column'}

```{.r .cell-code}
# Create tidy beta matrix
td_beta <- tidy(
  stm_mdl_k40, 
  method = "frex")

# Create top terms
top_terms <- td_beta %>%
  arrange(beta) %>%
  group_by(topic) %>%
  top_n(7, beta) %>%
  arrange(-beta) %>%
  select(topic, term) %>%
  summarise(terms = list(term)) %>%
  mutate(terms = map(
    terms,
    paste,
    collapse = ", ")) %>% 
  unnest(cols = c(terms))

# Output
top_terms
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}

