## Keyword co-occurrences

#### Brief introduction to bibliometrix



::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
keyword_matrix <- bibliometrix_data %>% 
  biblioNetwork(
    analysis = "co-occurrences",
    network = "keywords",
    sep = ";")

# Plot the network
net=keyword_matrix(
  NetMatrix,
  normalize="association",
  weighted=T, n = 30,
  Title = "Keyword Co-occurrences",
  type = "fruchterman",
  size=T,
  edgesize = 5,
  labelsize=0.7)
```
